      "notes": "Standard Nema17 stepper motor perfect for precise positioning in animatronics. Requires stepper driver (A4988, DRV8825, etc.). Excellent for head tracking, eye movement, jaw control, and other precise mechanical animations. Can rotate continuously in both directions with 1.8° precision.",
